		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Trapping code is a good idea. Thanks.<br /><br />My to-do list is like this(not necessarily in order):<br />1. Create HD pack for one action CHR ROM game. (Castlevania)<br />2. Create HD pack for one RPG CHR ROM game. (Dragonball Z)<br />3. Create HD pack for one action CHR RAM game. (1943)<br />4. Create HD pack for one RPG CHR RAM game. (Final Fantasy)<br />5. Add more mappers. (a few Konami mappers and MMC5)<br /><br />I want the internal working of the emulator to mature before adding scripting support. So I won't consider it until I have MMC5 working.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


